Terms of Use for images in the Josef Gugler African and Middle Eastern Film Collection:

The images in this collection are made available under an assertion of fair use (17 U.S.C. 107) and may be used only for non-commercial educational or research purposes. For permission to publish or otherwise reuse these images, please contact the Black Film Center/Archive (bfca@indiana.edu). Permission for publication is granted by Indiana University as the owner of the physical item and is not intended to include or imply permission of the copyright holder. The user is responsible for securing permission from the copyright owner and any other rights holders for any reuse of these images including reproduction and distribution. If you are the copyright holder for any of the digitized materials and have questions about its inclusion on our site, please contact the BFC/A staff at: bfca@indiana.edu.
